OL,3,CPontins owner charged with corporate
OL,4,Cmanslaughter after woman dies
OL,6,FThe owner of Pontins holiday parks has
OL,7,Fbeen charged with corporate
OL,8,Fmanslaughter after a woman died
OL,9,Ffollowing a ceiling collapse at Brean
OL,10,FSands resort.
OL,12,FWendy Jones, 68, was among 18 people
OL,13,Finjured when part of the air
OL,14,Fconditioning ducting fell from the
OL,15,Fceiling in February 2019. She died in
OL,16,Fhospital six months later.
OL,18,FFollowing an investigation by Avon and
OL,19,FSomerset Police and Somerset Council,
OL,20,Fthe CPS (Crown Prosecution Service)
OL,21,Fhas authorised the following charges:
