OL,6,FDetective Superintendent Roger Doxsey,
OL,7,Fsenior investigating officer, said:
OL,8,F"First and foremost our thoughts are
OL,9,Fwith the family of Wendy Jones. We
OL,10,Fhave updated them of the CPS' charging
OL,11,Fdecisions.
OL,13,F"This has been a complex investigation
OL,14,Fand we're grateful for the support of
OL,15,FSomerset Council and other partners to
OL,16,Freach this stage.
